                    <div style={{ padding: '9px 14px', fontSize: 12, color: grn, lineHeight: 1.55, borderBottom: '1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)' }}>Enable S3 Server-Side Encryption (SSE-S3, SSE-KMS) or use Client-Side Encryption.</div>
