                    <div style={{ padding: '9px 14px', fontSize: 12, color: grn, lineHeight: 1.55, borderBottom: '1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)' }}>Use Amazon Data Lifecycle Manager (DLM) to automate EBS snapshot creation.</div>
